Package fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.spaceTimeCoordinates

Class Time

java.lang.Object
fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.spaceTimeCoordinates.Time
public class Time extends Object
The Time class represents a point in time with specific attributes including day, month, year, hour, minute, and second. It provides methods for getting the current time, determining the start and end of previous months, and comparing time instances.
